---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/docs.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Install Airlock Cursor Enforcer">
    <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <img
                src="/enforcers/cursor.png"
                alt="Airlock Cursor Enforcer"
                class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl"
            />
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">
                    Airlock Cursor Enforcer
                </h1>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-1">
                    Human approval for AI actions in Cursor
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Prerequisites</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-link mt-1">•</span>
                    <span
                        ><a
                            href="https://www.cursor.com/"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="text-link hover:underline">Cursor</a
                        > IDE installed</span
                    >
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-link mt-1">•</span>
                    <span
                        >An Airlock account with at least one workspace
                        configured</span
                    >
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-link mt-1">•</span>
                    <span
                        >The Airlock Mobile Approver app installed on your phone
                        (Android or iOS)</span
                    >
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Installation</h2>
            <ol class="space-y-4 text-muted-foreground">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-airlock-violet/20 text-airlock-violet-light text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center"
                        >1</span
                    >
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-medium text-foreground">
                            Open Extensions
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                            In Cursor, open the Extensions panel by pressing <code
                                class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-muted text-xs font-mono"
                                >Ctrl+Shift+X</code
                            > (Windows/Linux) or <code
                                class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-muted text-xs font-mono"
                                >Cmd+Shift+X</code
                            > (macOS).
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-airlock-violet/20 text-airlock-violet-light text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center"
                        >2</span
                    >
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-medium text-foreground">
                            Search for Airlock
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                            In the search bar, type <code
                                class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-muted text-xs font-mono"
                                >Airlock Enforcer</code
                            >.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-airlock-violet/20 text-airlock-violet-light text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center"
                        >3</span
                    >
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-medium text-foreground">
                            Install the Extension
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                            Find <strong>Airlock Cursor Enforcer</strong> in the results
                            and click <strong>Install</strong>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-airlock-violet/20 text-airlock-violet-light text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center"
                        >4</span
                    >
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-medium text-foreground">
                            Configure Gateway URL
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                            Open Cursor settings (<code
                                class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-muted text-xs font-mono"
                                >Ctrl+,</code
                            >) and search for <code
                                class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-muted text-xs font-mono"
                                >airlock</code
                            >. Set the <strong>Gateway URL</strong> to your Airlock
                            gateway endpoint.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-airlock-violet/20 text-airlock-violet-light text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center"
                        >5</span
                    >
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-medium text-foreground">
                            Pair Your Device
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-1">
                            Use the Airlock Mobile Approver to pair your phone
                            with this workspace. The enforcer will intercept AI
                            actions and require your cryptographic approval
                            before execution.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                Once installed, the Airlock Cursor Enforcer intercepts all
                AI-generated terminal commands and file mutations. Each action
                is encrypted with AES-256-GCM and submitted to the Gateway. Your
                Mobile Approver receives a push notification — you review the
                action and sign your decision with Ed25519. The enforcer
                verifies the signature locally before allowing execution.
            </p>

            <div
                class="mt-8 p-4 rounded-xl border border-border/50 bg-muted/30"
            >
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                    <strong class="text-foreground">Security model:</strong> The enforcer
                    operates in fail-closed mode. If the gateway is unreachable, the
                    signature is invalid, or the request times out — the action is
                    blocked. No exceptions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
            <a href="/docs" class="text-sm text-link hover:underline"
                >← All Docs</a
            >
            <a href="/" class="text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:underline"
                >Back to Airlock</a
            >
        </div>
    </div>
</DocsLayout>
